@burin 
1) The current workflow (in master) assumes that Issuer needs to send 'Offer Credential' before the Traveler (Prover) sends 'Request Credential'
2) Traveler (Prover) NEVER send's credentials to the Verifier (Inspector), this is very essential. The Prover sends a *proof* created from credentials on the Prover side. Credntials are private and located in the Prover's wallet only.

